aott/analysis/escape_analysis/scalar_replacement.runa
Scalar Replacement of Aggregates Module for AOTT Optimization

This module provides scalar replacement optimization for the Runa AOTT system including:
- Aggregate object decomposition
- Field-to-scalar mapping
- Partial scalar replacement
- Array scalarization
- Structure flattening
- Reference elimination
- Load-store optimization
- Register promotion of fields
- Scalar replacement profitability
- Phi node generation for scalars
- Memory access pattern analysis
- Scalar lifetime management
- Debug info preservation
- Rematerialization support
- Cross-function scalar promotion
:End Note

Import "dev/debug/errors/core" as Errors

